[https://stedt.berkeley.edu/~stedt-cgi/rootcanal.pl/etymon/4459 STEDT] instead compares this word to {{cog|tbq-kuk-pro|*khooŋ|t=to beat}} and {{cog|tsj|ཀོང་མེ |t=to strike}}. Accepting STEDT's comparisons, this allows the reconstruction of {{inh|zh|sit-pro|*koŋ|t=to beat, strike}}.
